title: Spore Creature Pack - 3427 New Creatures [UT]
description:
3427 New Spore Creatures

This is intended for people who cannot access the online features or would prefer to play the game in offline mode. Adds 3427 new Spore creatures to your galaxy and does not contain the Fileplanet creature pack, this is all new stuff. 

Please help me seed this ! I can't do it alone :)
1. Extract the RAR to: "My Documents > My Spore Creations" Folder
OR 2. Drag all the .png's to your "Everything" Tab in game and SPORE automatically sorts it into the right folders for you (Alt+Enter - for windowed mode)
Enjoy !

- Unknown Terror
